title: Complete React Development Bootcamp
description: Master React from beginner to advanced with hands-on projects and real-world applications.
longDescription: This comprehensive course covers everything you need to know about React development, from basic concepts to advanced patterns. You'll build multiple projects, learn best practices, and gain the skills needed to create modern web applications.
instructorBio: Sarah has over 8 years of experience in web development and has worked with companies like Google and Meta.

title: Python for Data Science and Machine Learning
description: Learn Python programming and apply it to data science and machine learning projects.
longDescription: Dive deep into Python programming with a focus on data science applications. Learn pandas, numpy, matplotlib, and scikit-learn while building real machine learning models.
instructorBio: Michael is a senior data scientist with expertise in machine learning and statistical analysis.

title: UI/UX Design Fundamentals
description: Master the principles of user interface and user experience design with practical exercises.
longDescription: Learn the fundamentals of UI/UX design, including user research, wireframing, prototyping, and design systems. Perfect for beginners and those looking to transition into design.
instructorBio: Emily is a UX designer with 10 years of experience at leading design agencies and tech companies.

title: Digital Marketing Mastery
description: Complete guide to digital marketing including SEO, social media, and paid advertising.
longDescription: Learn all aspects of digital marketing from strategy to execution. Covers SEO, content marketing, social media marketing, email marketing, and paid advertising across platforms.
instructorBio: David has helped over 500 businesses grow their online presence and has managed marketing budgets over $10M.

title: Photography Composition and Lighting
description: Master the art of photography with advanced composition techniques and lighting setups.
longDescription: Take your photography to the next level with advanced composition techniques, lighting fundamentals, and post-processing workflows. Suitable for both portrait and landscape photography.
instructorBio: Lisa is an award-winning photographer with work featured in National Geographic and Vogue.

title: Music Production with Logic Pro
description: Create professional music tracks using Logic Pro with industry-standard techniques.
longDescription: Learn professional music production using Logic Pro. Covers recording, editing, mixing, and mastering techniques used in professional studios.
instructorBio: James has produced music for Grammy-winning artists and has over 15 years of studio experience.

title: Node.js Backend Development
description: Build scalable backend applications with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.
longDescription: Master backend development with Node.js. Learn to build RESTful APIs, work with databases, implement authentication, and deploy applications to production.
instructorBio: Sarah has over 8 years of experience in web development and has worked with companies like Google and Meta.

title: JavaScript Fundamentals
description: Master JavaScript from basics to advanced concepts with hands-on projects.
longDescription: A comprehensive introduction to JavaScript programming. Perfect for beginners who want to learn web development from the ground up.
instructorBio: Sarah has over 8 years of experience in web development and has worked with companies like Google and Meta.
